        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"William Kelley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n William Kelley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Guessing that was the Kalin Cuv\u00e9e CH? It\u2019s from the Charles Heintz vineyard in Sonoma. They split the fruit with Littorai, it was the first year Heintz was vineyard-designated.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Indeed. Just double checked, marked just over vintage on label. Thanks for the additional info! Excellent wine.</p>",
