        "created_at": "2018-05-04T18:19:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Good notes.</p>\n<p>I really liked that Kalin - no idea it was Charles Heintz! That makes sense.</p>\n<p>The 78 Corton, 99 Haut Brion, and the 05 Bonneau du Martray were all pretty spectacular and in great form.</p>\n<p>I think the Pousse d\u2019Or felt a little baked if I remember right - didn\u2019t match up to its potential for sure.</p>",
